## Re-running the wrapper

To pick up `.env` changes, restart the uvicorn process. To re-onboard from
scratch, re-launch the **Agent SDK Onboarder** and pick a different slug (a new
folder is generated each time).

## Troubleshooting

- **`/login` redirects but `/auth/callback` errors**: the redirect URI in your
  Entra app must include
  `http://${SERVER_HOST}:${SERVER_PORT}/auth/callback`. Add it under
  Authentication → Redirect URIs (Web).
- **`processContent` returns 401**: an admin still needs to grant consent on the
  Entra app's API permissions. Onboarder tried, but the signed-in user wasn't
  GA. Open `_onboarding-report.json` to see the consent URL.
- **Agent 365 spans return 401**: the Observability ingestion endpoint requires
  the agent to be managed by a Microsoft 1st-party application; for custom
  agents the spans currently stay in **console** mode (`ENABLE_A365_OBSERVABILITY_EXPORTER=false`).
